column5: Can we all bombard the state police and say we wont stop until he gets a much heavier sentence? This is simply unacceptable, we simply cannot accept this.
Would donate 60 percent to animals and the environment.  Takis shelter in greece is a favorite, dont know exactly the best environmental charities but would have to do research.

Thank you for the response - I try and tell myself these things but at the end of the day I am eaten alive by the negative emotion.  It wouldn't get me into legal trouble, and regardless of whether or not I deserve to live I don't know if I can live the rest of my life like this.  :(
Youre so brave to do this ‚ù§
